<div style="display: none;" class="drag-target">
  <h2>Add baby gear to your registry from any store on the Web</h2>
  <h3>Install the <strong>Add to Mamajamas</strong> bookmark.</h3>
  {{bookmarkletLink ''}}
  <ol>
    <li>
      Drag the button at left to your bookmarks bar.
      <div id="bookmark-arrow"></div>
    </li>
    <li>
      Find any product on the Web that you want to add to your baby gear registry.
    </li>
    <li>
      Click the “Add to Mamajamas“ button on your bookmark bar to add it to your registry.
    </li>
  </ol>
